History of Childhood Kidney Disease and Risk of Adult End-Stage Renal Disease.

Calderon-Margalit R(1), Golan E(1), Twig G(1), Leiba A(1), Tzur D(1), Afek A(1), 
Skorecki K(1), Vivante A(1).

Author information:
(1)From Hadassah-Hebrew University Braun School of Public Health (R.C.-M.) and 
