transcripts or ribonucleoproteins.

Liang Z(1)(2), Chen K(1), Zhang Y(1)(2)(3), Liu J(1), Yin K(4), Qiu JL(4), Gao 
C(1).

Author information:
(1)State Key Laboratory of Plant Cell and Chromosome Engineering, and Center for 
